- **Task 4 (Caller migration)** — file-bus.ts:344, session-log.ts:394, approval-bus.ts:245 + 447 all on `atomicRenameStaleDest`; approval-bus.ts:370 CLAIM migrated from raw `fsp.rename` to strict `atomicRename`.
- **Task 5 (Tests)** — 7 new tests for variant API surface; POSIX/Windows skip-conditionals correct; strict-EEXIST test asserts dst NOT overwritten + src still exists.
- **Task 6 (Telemetry)** — `atomic-rename-stale-dest-window` event added to discriminated union; emit fire-and-forget on Windows EEXIST recovery; basename-only privacy guard.
